news.title: China's first residential REITs to be launched soon
news.para: Stock exchanges in Shanghai and Shenzhen each accepted an application for residential REITs backed by rental incomes from affordable housing, exchange filings show.

news.title: Ahmedabad civic body files complaints against 18 commercial buildings
news.para: The city civic body has filed complaints against builders and managements of 18 commercial properties for failing to comply with fire safety norms.

news.title: Ludhiana: Property owners, councillor oppose demolition drive in Model Town
news.para: As the situation turned stormy, senior town planner Surinder Singh Bindra reached the spot in support of his staff. The councillor accused Bindra and his officials of encouraging encroachments in other parts of city.
